            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Neptuno <lb n="2"/>et Nymphis <lb n="3"/>pro salute <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>aris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Au<lb break="no" n="5"/><expan><abbr>rel</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> Anto<lb break="no" n="6"/>&amp;lt;nini<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> Anto<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/>&amp;gt;<lb break="no" n="7"/>nius Iulianus <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> V <expan><abbr>Luce</abbr><ex>nsium</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>posuit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nur handschriftlich überliefert. Z. 6: Text nach Vorschlag von J. Fitz vom Steinmetz oder Abschreiber offenbar versehentlich ausgelassen. Z. 7: überliefert ist AVLIANVS. Z. 8: überliefert ist COH VL V GE.</p>
            </div>
